{"type": "article", "id": 10108, "title": "Sensilk 可穿戴运动内衣", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-28T07:24:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607105817i1WvKodU6caYE7Ig.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tSensilk 是一件可穿戴的运动内衣,他们在普通运动内衣外面放了一个小型传感器，可以跟踪运动者的心率，呼吸，运动距离，消耗的卡路里等，搭配一个手机应用软件，可以计算出运动者的健身得分，为运动者进行健身建议。团队试图在保证技术的同时，保留运动内衣的轻便舒适和时尚的外观。目前售价 140 美元，<a href=\"http://sensilk.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105813E2S1OXJkmz7LcKDB.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.59571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071058135Ah2Q3a4IcXgyZxn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.62571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105814aVBg2T7iPoSRusz8.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.62571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105815WVyLxj5u734spX1U.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.59571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105816WoYuXMek3IVAliEK.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.59571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105816CMsAGS0T2aLwFcge.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.62571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}